Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:30.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The maidens that have gathered in Maria-sama's garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:35.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,pass through the tall gate once again today, carrying the pure visage of angels. {This is purposely changed from episode one. -Ky}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:40.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A deep colored sailor uniform envelopes their mind and bodies, which has no impurities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Keeping the pleats on one's skirt unruffled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:47.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Keeping the collar of the sailor uniform neat and tidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:49.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Walking slowly is preferred here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:52.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Private Lilian Girls Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is the garden of maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's only five minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:31.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,W-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,At this rate, soon the chance will be given to the absentee's to guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:39.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:58.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Please stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:25.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:35.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama, please forgive me for how rude I've been until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,In addition to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,would you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,make me your sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It is now 4:40. {times should be shown 4:40?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:19.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Because the time allowed is now over,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,those of you who've participated in the treasure hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,please assemble at the inner garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um... Everyone, we should hurry outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I just have to take it with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:37.57,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I want to confirm one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What will be done with the red card?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Er... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's Touko-chan's, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But, Rosa Chinensis...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I have no exclusive right to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:54.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I certainly did tell Yumi to stand up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:58.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but the one who actually made Yumi stand up was Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then please give the red card to Matsudaira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here are the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,As planned, after the hour for searching had passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:38.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Mami-san revealed the locations of the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:43.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako's white card was hidden underneath one of the teacher's cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and in the end, since no one had found her card,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:49.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,the winner will be the absentee who guessed the location of her card correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:55.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The yellow card was found for the second time in a row by Tanuma Chisato-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and Touko-chan became the winner of the red card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:05.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We personally handed out bite-sized chocolates to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.71,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Thanks for participating. {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:08.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,the participants who were unable to find the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.13,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Here you go. {Background.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thus, the Valentine's Day event,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,the treasure hunt for the next Roses' cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,ended safely, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:22.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,By the way, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:26.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:30.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes. Did you two talk about plans or called each other for the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There weren't any new developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll run over, and bring Touko-chan here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wai-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:44.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And if I get involved with this, things will become more complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:50.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um, Touko seems to have come to school, but she wasn't in class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:53.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It caused quite a stir,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and even I was cornered by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:59.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's become quite a big rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:00.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:06.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's better if I hurry and hand her the rosary, and formally make her my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We finally meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you, Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:38.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After taking a peek at the Drama club practicing in the gymnasium, I thought you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:42.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is about the date, isn't it? The date from the Valentine's Day event.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How does Sunday two weeks from now sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That day is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I pick the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:08:00.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course! It just has to stay within the budget of our day trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:02.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here. The details of the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The budget is two thousand yen per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:11.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Considering the cost of eating lunch, we won't be able to go too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:16.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But if we go to somewhere that's regular for students, we can get some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I have to tell her directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:38.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry. The two of you were in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It must be cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you would like, please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:45.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, thank you. Sorry for disturbing your club's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:46.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving soon, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:47.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:50.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to be that courteous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:52.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's just the two of us, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,See you then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um... Yumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:07.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Can you give me a reply after the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:35.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:40.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You told me that this would be a mystery tour, so you didn't tell me anything about today's date!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I was really troubled trying to decide what to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go. {was missing line, so i added it..think thats the tl}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,First, we'll take the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We took the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and arrived at a private train line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:12.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We took a train from there, and went to a different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The mystery tour that Touko-chan planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,took us farther and farther from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:36.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But up until now, Touko-chan has been rather silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:42.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My grandfather was incredibly overjoyed when he heard that I would inherit the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This happened a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:48.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hospital? Your grandfather's hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:50.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes, from my father's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:54.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But my father is a single child, and he isn't a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So then, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:04.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's a small hospital, but it's loved by the locals and the patients alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:07.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't want it to be closed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But my grandfather will be retiring in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then, what's going to happen to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:19.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's being taken care of by a husband and wife pair that had helped my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:24.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No one took me inheriting the hospital seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:30.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,In three years, I would have only just graduated from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm nowhere near obtaining a medical license.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:36.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought of marrying a doctor, but my parents were against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They said it was foolish to marry just for the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:44.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought that I wasn't needed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:49.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Since someone capable will be found, I had no business in getting involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:04.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:07.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I don't quite understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:11.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you so determined to inherit the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:14.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you not understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:17.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You can't trust the people who've come to take care of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, I can. They're very good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:27.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,For me, becoming a Matsudaira is more important than life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:28.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm slowly getting closer to Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:47.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan's heart must lie at the destination of this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's a bus for carrying patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My grandfather's hospital is far from the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Come on, take off your shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:32.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The bus from the station left the town, and entered a rural area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's almost noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:42.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Minus the money for the transportation back, we only have about six hundred yen between the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:45.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a convenience store near the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Uh, no! Um-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please wait little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Really, what am I thinking at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My mother's in this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. It suits your taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:33.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I get it! The hospital's cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:36.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We can eat within the budget here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:41.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:47.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I heard you were coming, but I had a house call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:49.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You look healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:55.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I heard you caused some trouble for your parents when you ran away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's quite grown up of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:59.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Really, that happened last year, grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:06.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is an upperclassman from my school, Fukuzawa Yumi-sama. {Missing name here xD}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, you said? Are you Sachiko-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:16.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes, Saiko-san speaks of her often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sachiko-sama's mother does?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:22.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see... So you're Yumi-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:27.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:30.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't take your eyes off of her for even one second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:31.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hello, Hashimoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:39.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,In the end, I was too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:43.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko told me the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:47.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"Because it's been there since you were young, you can't see the big picture."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:51.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:52.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're here to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:53.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So you come here sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:00.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:10.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How about we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sixteen years ago, there was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,On a gentle, descending curved road,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,a truck was forced into the opposite lane,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and crashed into a passenger car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:40.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The passenger car had a young husband and wife riding in it, they died due to the crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:50.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know the exact location, but it must have been around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:59.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A child that had just been born had been asleep in the child seat of the car, but the child was the only one that was saved without harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just like the baby just now-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:08.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, it was approximately one month after I was born, so I was even younger when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The lone baby that had been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,lost my parents once-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:31.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, please listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I lost my parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:40.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and my only relative was my grandmother on my father's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My grandmother was also hospitalized here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:51.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She couldn't raise me at all, so I was placed in an orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:57.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But all of a sudden, the Matsudaira's adopted me and raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My adopted mother is this person,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and this person...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This person's the one who gave birth to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:22.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The two of them were classmates in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:27.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I just found that out recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:33.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I knew from a long time ago that I wasn't the Matsudaira's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:37.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I overheard the talk of unsympathetic adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:40.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And so I thought:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:44.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If they had any bit of wisdom, they could find out by looking at the family register.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:50.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My birth mother had apparently performed plays with a small theater troop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:55.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When I knew that, I thought about dropping drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:00.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But if I suddenly quit, my parents might get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:06.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I love my current parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:13.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I cried when our opinions didn't match each other's when it came to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought I wasn't needed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:22.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Up until that point, my parents hadn't taken any interest in what I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:26.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:33.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to know everything about me, Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:40.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is the secret that Kashiwagi-san had talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:03.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I hated you, Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:07.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You were bright, innocent, and had everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:11.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And you looked like you were never affected by anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:14.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Well, I get as confused as anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I understand that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:17.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:22.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:24.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:27.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I even thought that I shouldn't be near you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:34.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But you steadily broke down the wall I had so desperately tried to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Can you not talk about others as if they're monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:39.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:44.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,At the time, the rumor that I was a candidate to become your sister was spreading, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:48.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,All I did was make you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There was no way I could become your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:54.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I denied it frantically in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but, on the contrary, you were looking out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:01.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's why I ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:07.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even then, you suddenly asked me: "Will you become my sister?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:11.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:27.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She could have just released all of the one-sided emotions she had collected inside herself fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll listen to any number of complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:37.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After all, we'll become sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:42.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After feeling refreshed from spilling everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:46.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll fill an open part of her heart with happy memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:50.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just like how I did with Sachiko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:02.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please wait just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:06.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we'll go to school, and then... {we'll make love!}
